title: Draft picks we want to see
itunes:title: Draft picks we want to see
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Jarvis Landry predicting the Dolphins will sweep the Patriots in 2017, and defensive end Dion Jordan signing with the Seahawks. Then the heroes talk about the best fits for some of the most high profile, day-one draft prospects. Plus, we hash out the great Wesselmania cornhole controversy of 2017.
